{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"🤔️ Jason Yang's Blog","author":"Jason Yang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"5c04baca-1dc5-51a4-8898-385ff2b3e3ec","excerpt":"MySQL for Mac 默认 bin log 是关闭的，使用以下命令查看 bin log 是否开启：Variable_nameValuelog_binOFF修改/etc/my.conf，没有文件就新建一个，添加以下配置：重启MySQL，再次查看 bin log 状态：Variable_nameValuelog…","html":"<p>MySQL for Mac 默认 bin log 是关闭的，使用以下命令查看 bin log 是否开启：</p>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--sql\"><span>SHOW&nbsp;VARIABLES&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--other syntax--DML syntax--sql\"><span>LIKE</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--string syntax--quoted syntax--single syntax--sql\"><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--begin syntax--sql\"><span>&#39;</span></span><span>log_bin&#39;</span></span><span>;</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Variable_name</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>log_bin</td>\n<td>OFF</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>修改/etc/my.conf，没有<code class=\"language-text\">my.conf</code>文件就新建一个，添加以下配置：</p>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--text syntax--plain syntax--null-grammar\"><span>[mysqld]</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--text syntax--plain syntax--null-grammar\"><span>log-bin=mysql-bin&nbsp;#添加这一行就ok</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--text syntax--plain syntax--null-grammar\"><span>binlog-format=ROW&nbsp;#选择row模式</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--text syntax--plain syntax--null-grammar\"><span>server_id=1&nbsp;#配置mysql&nbsp;replaction需要定义，不能和canal的slaveId重复</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<p>重启MySQL<code class=\"language-text\">系统偏好设置-&gt;MySQL-&gt;Stop MySQL Server -&gt; Start MySQL Server</code>，再次查看 bin log 状态：</p>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--sql\"><span>SHOW&nbsp;VARIABLES&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--other syntax--DML syntax--sql\"><span>LIKE</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--string syntax--quoted syntax--single syntax--sql\"><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--begin syntax--sql\"><span>&#39;</span></span><span>log_bin&#39;</span></span><span>;</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Variable_name</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>log_bin</td>\n<td>ON</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","frontmatter":{"title":"Mac 下 MySQL 开启 bin log","date":"2018-07-23"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/open-mysql-binlog-for-mac/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/docker-practice-notes/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Docker Practice Notes 01"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/ssh-proxy/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"开启ssh代理服务"}}}}